display_long_description:
With **core gameplay of Dungeon crawlers**, this game brings you into a world full of surprises. Explore random dungeons, fight tough enemies, and survive intense battles. Every moment brings new challenges and adventure!      
                                                                                                                                                           
[media]

**Full Game:** 
**meta.com/experiences/6743334779111805**

 **discord.gg/pdvr** join to win gifts🎁

# 💥Boss Fight, Awesome Every Time
Skull King slashes his axe. Ghost Lord causes explosions & shoots bullets to chase you! Angel turns into giant monster & unleashes deadly lasers. God of Time shatters the ground & throws everyone into a new battleground where the action only intensifies! 
[media]

# ⚔️Rich Weapons, Always Something New
- Crash through enemies with Captain America's shield! Unleash Wolverine's claws to rip apart monsters!
- **Level up your gear!** 2 stars to 3 stars? Double damage, double chaos! [media]

# 👑Tons of Hero Looks, Customize Yours!
Choose from The Witcher, Black Knight, Bird Man... and more
[media]

# ✨Free Version - Still Fun!
- **Endless Exploration**: Explore random maps and rich scenes-adventure awaits!
- **Fight monsters together**: exciting team action! Rock-paper-scissors in the dungeon? tons of laughs!
- **Monster chaos**: Slimes bounce, spiders crawl-explore their nests and crush them all! 
[media]
